As a reminder, please categorize each TARGET word (the SECOND stimulus presented) as QUICKLY and ACCURATELY as possible by pressing:

the left ('E') key if the target word is BAD.
or
the right ('I') key if the target word is GOOD.

After categorizing the target word, remember to recite the MEMORY word (the FIRST stimulus presented). Please speak clearly but not too loudly. 

If you have any questions, please ask them to the experimenter now before you move on the actual experiment."
</item>

<text readyblock1UP>
